item.title: EP 126 - Where Do Missing People Go?
item.itunes:title: Where Do Missing People Go?
item.description:
Russian bots, the worst sports disaster in world history, and you’ve heard of mysterious disappearances but what about mysterious appearances!

Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

Russian 24, the State-controlled media outlet, recently claimed one of the advanced humanoid robots ever created was ready for prime time. But was there something else that powered that bot?

Then we go back in time to explore the worst sports disaster in world history. The more things change . . .

And finally, we investigate the mysterious reappearance of man who went missing for 15 months.

Links:

Robot turns out to be man in suit

https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-46538126

The Steven Kubacki Encounter And The Reappearance Mysteries

https://www.ufoinsight.com/the-steven-kubacki-encounter-and-the-reappearance-mysteries/

The Mysterious Disappearance of Steven Kubacki, and his odd reappearance 15 months later.

https://coolinterestingstuff.com/the-mysterious-disappearance-of-steven-kubacki-and-his-odd-reappearance-15-months-later
